                    <note>This incipit is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="BDLaethb4"/>.</note>
                    <ab>፳፡ ተአምሪሁ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="SH"/> ወሀሎ፡ ፩ እኩይ፡ በሀገረ፡ ብባ፡ ወአረሚ፡
